{"word":"Absalom","slug":"absalom","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Absalom</b> <a href=\"#/H53\">H53</a> <br/> Called also Abishalom.<br/> Son of David by Maacah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=3'>2Sa 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=2'>1Ch 3:2</a><br/> Beauty of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=25'>2Sa 14:25</a><br/> Slays Amnon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=29'>2Sa 13:29</a><br/> Flees to Geshur<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=13&verse=38'>2Sa 13:38</a><br/> Is permitted by David to return to Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=24'>2Sa 14:24</a><br/> His demagogism<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=6'>2Sa 15:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15&verse=13'>2Sa 15:13</a><br/> Conspiracy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=15'>2Sa 15</a><br/> Death and burial<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=17'>2Sa 18:17</a><br/> David's mourning for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=33'>2Sa 18:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=8'>2Sa 19:8</a><br/> Children of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=27'>2Sa 14:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=18'>2Sa 18:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=2'>1Ki 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=20'>2Ch 11:20</a><br/> Pillar of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=18'>2Sa 18:18</a>"}]}